---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import PageHero from "../components/PageHero.astro";

import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import NGIPhoto from "../assets/ngi-website.png";
import Banner from "../components/Banner.astro";

---



<MainLayout title="Winnard | NGI Project">

<!-- ==================== Project hero =============== -->
<PageHero>
    <h1 class="max-w-2xl mb-4 text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-none md:text-5xl xl:text-6xl">Northern Girl Initiative</h1>
                <p class="text-center">I had the pleasure of working on a project for NGI, a remarkable NGO dedicated to advancing girls' education and empowerment programs across Northern Ghana.

                </p>
</PageHero>
<!-- end of project hero -->



<!-- ======================== Project Information ====================== -->
<section class="section-info py-20 md:py-36">
    <div class="container wrapper">
        <!-- Project Image -->
        <Image src={NGIPhoto} alt="NGI Website" />

        <div class="info-container py-20">
            <!-- Side navigation -->
            <div class="sidenav">
                <ul class="sidenav-list">
                    <li class="sidenav-item">
                        <h1>client</h1>
                        <p>Northern Girl Initiative</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="sidenav-item">
                        <h1>services</h1>
                        <p>Website Copywriting &amp; Blogs</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="sidenav-item">
                        <h1>Website</h1>
                        <p>
                            <a href="https://northerngirlinitiative.org/" target="_blank">Live Preview &UpperRightArrow;</a>
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <!-- End of side navigation -->

            <div class="info-content">
                <!-- About the project -->
                <h1 class="max-w-2xl mb-4 text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-none md:text-5xl xl:text-6xl dark:text-white">About the project</h1>
                <p>My role involved copywriting for their entire website, ensuring the content reflected NGI's mission and vision while resonating with visitors. </p>

                <ol class="ml-4 list-decimal my-4 mb-20">
                    <li> I took the time to deeply understand NGI's mission and values, ensuring that the content accurately reflected their dedication to girls' education and empowerment.</li>
                    <li> NGI's brand identity was in every piece of text, making sure the copy was consistent and aligned with their core message.</li>
                    <li> The copy was crafted to be welcoming and informative, aiming to engage visitors and encourage them to support NGI's initiatives.</li>
                    <li> I clearly conveyed NGI's mission and vision, helping visitors understand the impact of NGI's work on the communities of Northern Ghana.</li>
                    <li>Through the various pages, I highlighted NGI's efforts in helping girls complete their education, pursue careers, and advocate for equal rights, showcasing the power of girls to create positive change.</li>
                </ol>


                <!-- Goal of the project -->
                <h1 class="max-w-2xl mb-4 text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-none md:text-5xl xl:text-6xl dark:text-white">What was the goal of the project?</h1>
                <p>The main goal was to create a compelling and informative website that effectively communicated NGI's mission to empower Northern Ghana girls through education and advocacy, thereby attracting support and engagement from the community and potential donors.</p>

                <Image src={NGIPhoto} alt="NGI Website" class="my-8 mb-20" />

                <!-- Project Execution -->
                <h1 class="max-w-2xl mb-4 text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-none md:text-5xl xl:text-6xl dark:text-white">Project Execution</h1>
                <p class="mb-20">Working on this website was an exciting one! I started with a deep dive into their mission, ensuring every word reflected their dedication to empowering girls in Northern Ghana. By embodying their brand identity, I wrote content that was not only informative but also warmly welcoming. I made sure the tone was engaging, encouraging visitors to interact and support the cause. The clear communication of their mission and vision helped visitors understand the impact of NGIâ€™s work. Ultimately, the content highlighted NGI's incredible efforts in education and advocacy, showcasing the transformative power of their initiatives in a way that was both inspiring and easy to grasp.</p>

                <!-- project Outcome -->
                <h1 class="max-w-2xl mb-4 text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-none md:text-5xl xl:text-6xl dark:text-white">Project Outcome</h1>
                <p> This was definitely an incredibly rewarding and educational experience for me. The clients were super happy with the outcome, praising how the content embodied their brand identity. This project not only enhanced NGI's online presence but also played a crucial role in advancing their mission to empower young girls.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<!-- End of Project Information -->


<Banner></Banner>

</MainLayout>





<style lang="scss">


.info-container {
    width: 100%;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: auto;
    gap: 8;
}


/* Sticky Side Navigation */ 
.sidenav {
    width: 100%;
    // height: 100%;
    

    .sidenav-list {
        position: sticky;
        top: 100px;
        left: 0;
    }
    .sidenav-item {

        &:not(:last-child) {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #5D5D5D;
            font-weight: 400;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            color: rgb(var(--clr-win-blue));
            transition: .2s;

            &:hover, &:focus {
                transform: translateX(10px);
            }
        }
    }
}

.info-content {
    grid-column: span 4 / span 4;
}






// ==================================== MEDIA QUERRIES ======================
@media screen and (max-width: 765px) {
    .info-container {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 3rem;;
    }


    // Side nav
    .sidenav {
        
        .sidenav-list {
            position: static;
        }
    }
}
</style>